instances.text: CPSC_V 203-201 - Programming, Problem Solving, and Algorithms

detailResultFields.label: Course Section Definition Public Notes
detailResultFields.value:
Due to unfixable technical issues, Workday Student is unable to manage the labs for CPSC 203. Therefore registration in the CPSC 203 lecture section is contingent on availability for an appropriate lab section and space in the lab. Please see the list below for details on when and where labs are expected at. The course staff will work with students to find a suitable lab time in the first week of classes. Students who cannot find a suitable lab time will unfortunately need to be de-registered from the course

CPSC 203.L2A | Tue | 12:30  4 PM | ICCS X351
CPSC 203.L2B | Mon | 12PM  1:30PM | ICCS X351
CPSC 203. L2C | Tue | 5PM  6:30 PM | ICCS X350
CPSC 203.L2D | Tue | 4 PM  5:30 PM | ICCS X351
CPSC 203.L2E | Tue | 5:30 PM  7:00 PM | ICCS X351
